  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>ePRO Validation</measure>
    <time_frame>7 months</time_frame>
    <description>To evaluate measurement equivalence between the two PRO data collection modes - original paper mode versus the ePRO application on a handheld mobile phone for the following PRO's: SF-36 HRQoL questionnaire, the FACIT-F fatigue instrument, and the PtGA. The three PROs will be administered on clinic days by both modes: paper and ePRO. Concurrent results will be compared, and percentage similarities calculated.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
